    data-social-hash-id=""
    data-social-blurb="Hugh%20Bonneville%20%28Lord%20Grantham%20on%20%22Downton%20Abbey%22%29%20delivers%20one%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20performances%20as%20an%20alcoholic%20British%20art%20historian%2C%20seeking%20noble%20redemption%20as%20part%20of%20the%20small%2C%20multi-national%20squad%20headed%20by%20Fogg%20Museum%20curator%2Fconservationist%20Frank%20Stokes%20%28George%20Clooney%29%2C%20who%20is%20determined%20to%20preserve%20Europe%27s%20greatest%20works%20of%20art%20from%20acquisition%20and%2For%20destruction%20in%201944%20by%20the%20retreating%20Nazis.%0A%0ABlanchett%27s%20character%20is%20based%20on%20French%20Resistance%20leader%20Rose%20Valland%2C%20whose%20memoir%20inspired%20John%20Frankenheimer%27s%20%22The%20Train.%22%0A%0AJason%20and%20Daniel%20are%20both%20single%2C%20designing%20book%20covers%20at%20the%20same%20trendy%20downtown%20publishing%20company%2C%20while%20Mikey%20is%20an%20emergency%20room%20doctor.%0A%0ADebuting%20writer%2Fdirector%20Tom%20Gormican%2C%20whose%20previous%20credit%20is%20as%20producer%20on%20the%20dreadful%20%22Movie%2043%2C%22%20sets%20up%20a%20crude%2C%20immature%20male%20version%20of%20the%20dating%20experience%2C%20often%20substituting%20frenetic%20pace%20for%20intelligent%20insight%20on%20the%20sensitive%20issue%20of%20commitment.%0A%0A%5B...%5D%20it%27s%20not%20surprising%20that%20the%20female%20characters%20are%20sketchily%20underwritten%20and%20ill-served%2C%20while%20an%20inordinate%20amount%20of%20screen%20time%20is%20devoted%20to%20male%20genitalia%3A%0A%0ASince%20it%20was%20published%20in%201818%2C%20Mary%20Shelley%27s%20classic%20literary%20creation%20has%20had%20many%20screen%20incarnations%20but%20few%20as%20ridiculous%20as%20Stuart%20Beattie%27s%20convoluted%20concept%20of%20using%20him%20as%20an%20invaluable%20pawn%20in%20the%20perennial%20battle%20between%20good%20and%20evil%2C%20represented%20by%20gargoyles%20and%20demons.%0A%0AWandering%20the%20world%20alone%20and%20pursued%20by%20demons%2C%20he%27s%20dubbed%20Adam%20and%20offered%20shelter%20in%20a%20massive%2C%20medieval%20Gothic%20cathedral%20by%20Gargoyle%20Queen%20Leonore%20%28Miranda%20Otto%29%2C%20who%20recognizes%20him%20as%20a%20fellow%20outsider%2C%20noting%2C%20%22Humans%20think%20of%20us%20as%20mere%20decoration.%22%0A%0AFilled%20with%20reams%20of%20expository%20dialogue%2C%20choppily-edited%20fights%2C%20an%20invasive%20musical%20score%20and%20lots%20of%20CGI-enhanced%20transformations%2C%20it%20resembles%20an%20incoherent%20video%20game."
